rce-header__content-title \">How Rhone Curated a Seamless E-Commerce Experience with Stylitics</h2>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-header__content-footer\">\n                  </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>	\n	<div class=\"o-container\">\n		<div class=\"single__body\">\n			<div class=\"single__content ui-blocks \">\n				<div class=\"ui-blocks__content\">\n					\n<p>Rhone wanted to elevate their online shopping experience to reflect the thoughtfully curated, outfit-driven approach of their in-store merchandising. They aimed to encourage product discovery, showcase a new women&#8217;s line, enhance cart size, improve upsell opportunities, and increase revenue without compromising brand identity. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>By partnering with Stylitics, Rhone was able to create an AI-powered, curated shopping experience that seamlessly aligned with their brand values.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Results</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>39% increase in average order value (AOV) driven by curated outfit recommendations.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>10x ROI within the first 100 days of launching Shop the Model.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Improved conversion rates: 13% for men’s collections and 8% for women’s collections.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>&#8220;Stylitics has helped us bridge the gap between our online and in-store experience, creating a path to product discovery and inspiring our customers with premium, curated looks.&#8221;</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p><em>— Emily Heger, Director, Digital Product at Rhone</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;re excited to see Rhone deliver shopping experiences that spark inspiration, build loyalty, and drive measurable growth in conversions and cart value. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://stylitics.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stylitics-x-Rhone-Case_study.pdf\">Download the full case study</a></strong> to learn more about how Stylitics drives improvements in conversions and AOV.</p>\n	\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"single__footer\">\n  <a class=\"single__footer-nav\" href=\"https://stylitics.com/resources/case-studies/\">\n    <?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 17\" fill=\"none\">\n  <g opacity=\"0.7\">\n    <path d=\"M1.23077 8.63151H16M1.23077 8.63151L8.64033 15.2982M1.23077 8.63151L8.64033 1.96484\" stroke=\"#001524\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg>\n    <span>Back to Case Studies</span>\n  </a>\n\n  <div class=\"single__share\">\n	<div class=\"single__share-title\">Share this</div>\n	<div class=\"single__share-icons\">\n      \n      <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&#038;url=https://stylitics.com/resources/case-studies/how-rhone-curated-a-seamless-e-commerce-experience-with-stylitics/&#038;title=How%20Rhone%20Curated%20a%20Seamless%20E-Commerce%20Experience%20with%20Stylitics\" class=\"single__share-icon single__share-icon--linkedin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"Share on LinkedIn\">\n        <?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"33\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 33\" fill=\"none\">\n  <rect y=\"0.760742\" width=\"31.9253\" height=\"31.9253\" rx=\"15.9627\" fill=\"#001524\"></rect>\n  <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.0482 10.0723H20.877C21.6525 10.0723 22.2811 10.734 22.2811 11.5503V21.8965C22.2811 22.7128 21.6525 23.3745 20.877 23.3745H11.0482C10.2727 23.3745 9.64404 22.7128 9.64404 21.8965V11.5503C9.64404 10.734 10.2727 10.0723 11.0482 10.0723ZM13.1543 21.1574C13.3482 21.1574 13.5054 20.992 13.5054 20.7879V15.6149C13.5054 15.4108 13.3482 15.2453 13.1543 15.2453H12.1013C11.9074 15.2453 11.7502 15.4108 11.7502 15.6149V20.7879C11.7502 20.992 11.9074 21.1574 12.1013 21.1574H13.1543ZM12.6278 14.5063C12.0462 14.5063 11.5747 14.01 11.574