lock-heading\">What Clients Say</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|20\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><em>\"The very FIRST content Alex wrote for HydroPoint came back as a winner! Great job Alex!\"</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">– Meg Mason, VP Marketing, HydroPoint</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|20\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><em>“This is GREAT. THANK YOU for making this happen for Stylitics; most sincerely appreciated. Alex, please work with the team to make more of these [case studies]!”</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"> – Casey Birtwell, CRO, Stylitics</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|20\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><em>\"You are essentially operating as the Lead Producer on all of our content related to this event. That is super impressive- we are getting it all done, bc of your watchful eye and attention to these million moving pieces. I wanted to say 1) thank you!! For everything you’re doing, and 2) do you realize that you are very good at this? You should 😉”</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">- Sari Green, CMO, Winning by Design</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|20\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><em>”Thank you for the help [producing the Revenue Architecture textbook]. Your help made all the difference and i won’t forget it. 🙏”</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">– Jacco van der Kooij, Founder &amp; CEO, Winning by Design</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|70\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|70\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--70);padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Let\'s Connect</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ready to elevate your content? Let’s talk.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>📧   <a href=\"mailto:alexeresser@gmail.com\">alexeresser@gmail.com</a><br>🔗   <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/alex-esser-435921158/\">LinkedIn</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2025-03-06 02:34:26','2025-03-06 02:34:26','',10,'http://alexanderesser.local/?p=85',0,'revision','',0);
